00:21:42,802 --> 00:21:44,395
You ridiculous man.

280
00:21:44,553 --> 00:21:48,729
Now, what do we do about
your dear, dear, gun-toting father?

281
00:21:48,891 --> 00:21:50,939
I've been thinking about that.

