430
00:31:03,445 --> 00:31:06,790
"Find Darkness and Decay
and the Red Death

431
00:31:06,948 --> 00:31:09,292
"held illimitable dominion over all. "

432
00:31:14,706 --> 00:31:18,336
So this gentleman dresses up
like a... what? Like a...

