the inspiration to an actual killer.

471
00:33:55,283 --> 00:33:56,660
Quite gruesome, really.

472
00:33:56,826 --> 00:33:59,545
If I'd known my work had
a morbid effect on people,

473
00:33:59,704 --> 00:34:01,502
