486
00:34:31,653 --> 00:34:33,246
Does it? Why?

487
00:34:33,405 --> 00:34:38,411
How else should Edgar Allan Poe
commit himself to eternal love

488
00:34:38,577 --> 00:34:41,376
other than under threat of death?

489
00:34:42,998 --> 00:34:44,625
