You coward!

1010
01:17:31,897 --> 01:17:33,991
{GUNSHOT RICOCHETS}

1011
01:17:35,192 --> 01:17:36,819
Who are you?!

1012
01:17:41,699 --> 01:17:43,417
{GUNSHOT}

1013
01:17:54,170 --> 01:17:56,047
-{HORSE HOOVES}
